  "content": "\n<p>As I mentioned in a previous post, I’m a little anchor obsessed right now! With that in mind, I scoured other Etsy shops for fun anchor themed items: art, jewelry, home decor and more. I hope you like the treasury I put together!</p>\n<p>If you love the items above and want to check out the individual shops, you can find them each below! For a direct link to the treasury (to leave it some love!) you can <strong><a title=\"Anchor's Away on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNjMwODczOA/anchors-away\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">see it here on Etsy</a></strong>.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Kitty Meow Boutique Anchor Card\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/100045726/navy-anchor-cards-you-are-my-anchor-qty?ref=tre-2726308738-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kitty Meow Boutique</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Clair Ashley Anchor Ring\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/66864390/anchor-ring-hand-stamped-ring-nautical?ref=tre-2726308738-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Clair Ashley</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Friendly Oak Anchor Tank\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/129218036/anchor-tank-top-nautical-sailor-american?ref=tre-2726308738-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Friendly Oak</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Haven By Laura Anchor Pillow\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/179622068/hand-painted-burlap-anchor-pillow-14x14?ref=tre-2726308738-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Haven By Laura</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Tie Obsessed anchor tie\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/95509826/tie-navy-blue-anchor-nautical-stripe?ref=tre-2726308738-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tie Obsessed</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Graphic Variete digital anchor transfer\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/126200348/anchor-sail-ocean-sailing-boat-digital?ref=tre-2726308738-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Graphic Variete</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Secret Find anchor earrings\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/158953698/anchor-earrings-anchor-jewelry-stud?ref=tre-2726308738-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Secret Find</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Roberta Valle anchor necklace\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/168465694/anchor-dainty-necklace-anchor-jewelry?ref=tre-2726308738-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Roberta Valle</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Household Words anchor decal\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/125607978/anchor-decor-and-birds-flying-decal-wall?ref=tre-2726308738-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Household Words</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Secret Find anchor cufflinks\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/90479851/sea-cufflinks-blue-anchor-anchor-jewelry?ref=tre-2726308738-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Secret Find</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"White Apple Design anchor tote\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/176507981/eco-friendly-nautical-anchor-market-tote?ref=tre-2726308738-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">White Apple Designs</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Vespertina Vi anchor ring\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/174096458/back-in-stock-anchoring-anchor-ring?ref=tre-2726308738-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vespertina Vi</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Vintage Affair Studio anchor pillow\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/117482227/in-high-tide-or-low-tide-anchor-pillow?ref=tre-2726308738-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vintage Affair Studio</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Wall Art Boutique anchor art\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/185364516/nautical-nursery-wall-art-nursery-wall?ref=tre-2726308738-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wall Art Boutique</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Jade Journey anchor key fob\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/111253605/seersucker-anchor-monogram-wristlet-key?ref=tre-2726308738-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jade Journey</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Graphic Spaces Wood anchor bookend\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/106775491/wood-anchor-bookend-nautical-boat-anchor?ref=tre-2726308738-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Graphic Spaces Wood</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Which item is your fave? Are you completely obsessed with something right now too, like I am with anchors?</p>\n",
